<p>The <code>page</code> tag includes another page.</p>

<h2>Include a Subpage</h2>
<pre>{open}page 'fragments/claude/subpage'{close}</pre>
{page 'fragments/claude/subpage'}

<h2>Include with Variable Passing</h2>
<pre>{open}page 'fragments/claude/subpage', $subpageMessage='Custom message'{close}</pre>
{page 'fragments/claude/subpage', $subpageMessage='Custom message passed via page tag'}

<h2>Include Snippets from _include</h2>
<pre>{open}greeting{close}</pre>
{greeting}

<pre>{open}snippet{close}</pre>
{snippet}

<h2>Scope Options</h2>
<pre>{open}page 'path', sandbox{close}  {open}!-- isolated scope --{close}
{open}page 'path', clean{close}    {open}!-- clean scope --{close}</pre>
<p>These options control variable scope when including pages.</p>
